they could scarce hear one another: (^Allen^) to appease the
multitude, flung handfuls of money among them: saying,$]
(^Good people forbear comming any farther^) , and be civil: for
we are Gentlemen: and to the contrary expect death some of
you: [^---^]
[^ALLEN AND HIS MEN MANAGE TO ESCAPE TO AN INN SOME TWENTY MILES
