[} (^HOW^) HIND (^ROBBED A GENTLEMAN OF ONE HUNDRED AND FIFTY POUNDS,
NEAR NOTTINGHAM^) .}]

   [$Hind travelling up and down at last met with a lusty
young fellow whom he had formerly known: and
asking him many questions, among the rest: said,$] (^Jack, If thou
